{"tid":528585,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"窗台房　機艙廁　前業主屢創「奇則」","createTime":"2018-01-14T03:38:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T04:10:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"78da70a3dfa97367ff148f4b908ba32bf5fd9830","tid":528585,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T03:38:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180114/20273879\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180114%2F20273879&d=ORkV3TibX6eVz69FFHa7AAHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=22b7067c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180114%2F20273879&h=80f59485\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180114/20273879</a><br />\n<br />\n窗台房　機艙廁　前業主屢創「奇則」<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180114/large/14la4p05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180114%2Flarge%2F14la4p05.jpg&h=4a2b3925&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n建築師梁世雄曾設計屯門海譽窗台佔過半面積的工人房。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】鄭若驊持有的海詩別墅四號屋，是從建築師梁世雄手上購下。梁世雄涉嫌曾在該物業進行僭建工程，令樓價翻倍，賺逾千萬離場。本身與多間發展商合作設計住宅項目的梁世雄，過往筆下的住宅項目不乏爭議「奇則」，包括要睡窗台的工人房、14呎的「機艙廁」、呎價逼近3萬元的「劏房盤」等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n設計呎價2.9萬元劏房盤<br />\n<br />\n本身是屋宇署認可人士的梁世雄，1985年與建築師馬思儉合組馬梁建築師事務所，長期與多間發展商合作設計住宅項目，亦有承接其他工商廈、學校、市區重建等項目。由梁世雄任認可人士的住宅項目，過去不乏富爭議的設計，例如2012年屯門長實項目「海譽」，就出現窗台佔過半面積的工人房，必須將半邊床放上窗台才有機會放得下。<br />\n<br />\n2015年長和的將軍澳緻藍天，就有4房4廁、全屋13道門的「奇則」單位，雖然單位面積有1,100呎，但4個廁所中有3個都是不見天日的黑廁，其中客廁更只得14呎，窄得有如飛機上的「機艙廁」；間隔亦被網民譏諷「方便間作劏房」。<br />\n<br />\n梁世雄亦有設計真正的「劏房盤」，前年入伙宏基資本尖沙嘴項目「匯萃」，單位面積僅得210至222呎，屬「全開放式」單位，但年前樓花的叫價卻高至每呎2.9萬，被批評為「劏房盤豪宅價」。 <br />\n<br />\n■記者林偉聰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180114/large/14la4p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180114%2Flarge%2F14la4p04.jpg&h=868139bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n建築師梁世雄<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n\t劉兆佳引述中央官員鄭若驊僭建　京促港妥善解決免損威信<br />\n要聞 5小時前"},{"pid":"72acda25a114c3dff8f6c1969b48429da0fb3078","tid":528585,"uid":25822,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T03:40:15.000Z","msg":"呢啲人快啲仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bed69ac5a4f22406fa76d193784281045b5c2d6","tid":528585,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T03:52:55.000Z","msg":"咁叫建築師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4871431ccc7abdb89192b98abd74cc0da179e9ce","tid":528585,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T03:58:24.000Z","msg":"間工人房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想殺左老細"},{"pid":"84802705d652baaf1443816104e34b143449e2b9","tid":528585,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T04:01:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6afd7d44944f3944c18c8def9e57bf70d08ba995","tid":528585,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72acda25a114c3dff8f6c1969b48429da0fb3078","tid":528585,"uid":25822,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T03:40:15.000Z","msg":"呢啲人快啲仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"